## Project overview
This project performs exploratory analysis, modelling, and visualization on a realistic loan-approval dataset to produce actionable insights about which applicant and loan features most influence approval decisions. The visualizations are designed to be interpretable for both technical and non-technical stakeholders.
## Motivation
Loan decisions can be opaque. By combining EDA, predictive baselines, and thoughtfully designed visualizations, this project aims to:
- Highlight the dominant factors affecting approvals
- Help lenders detect bias or unexpected patterns
- Empower applicants to know which features to improve

